Package com.tenio.common.data.common

Class CommonArray

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
java.util.AbstractList<E>
java.util.ArrayList<Object>
com.tenio.common.data.common.CommonArray
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Object>, Collection<Object>, List<Object>, RandomAccess
public final class CommonArray extends ArrayList<Object> implements Serializable
This is an element array class holds data in a map. All message comes from other services will be converted to this object. That helps normalize the way to communicate and be easy to use.
